summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 232W, page 26, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in North Park Addition, Lots 15 and 16, Block 2, Lots 12 and 13, Block 7, and all of Blocks 21 and 22, as Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone.
